    <h1 class="title">Developing Data Products - Project Assignment</h1>
  <h1 class="subtitle">Stock Prediction and Analysis</h1>
    <h2 class="author">Bernard Lei</h2>
    <h3 class="date">September 20, 2016</h3>
</section>

<section class="slide level2">

<p>OBJECTIVE:</p>
<p>Develop an application to predict and analyze a stock or index: Use of various widgets of the Shiny tool Understand the process of publishing application in Shiny Interface with Shiny tool, using ui.R and server.R code.</p>
<p>Example of ui.R code: Sidebar for a stock quote</p>
<div class="sourceCode"><pre class="sourceCode r"><code class="sourceCode r"><span class="kw">library</span>(shiny)</code></pre></div>
<pre><code>## Warning: package 'shiny' was built under R version 3.2.5</code></pre>
<div class="sourceCode"><pre class="sourceCode r"><code class="sourceCode r"><span class="kw">shinyUI</span>(<span class="kw">fluidPage</span>(<span class="kw">sidebarPanel</span>(
      <span class="kw">textInput</span>(<span class="st">"caption"</span>, <span class="st">"Enter the stock symbol"</span>, <span class="st">""</span>))))</code></pre></div>
<div class="container-fluid">
<div class="col-sm-4">
<form class="well">
<div class="form-group shiny-input-container">
<label for="caption">Enter the stock symbol</label>
<input id="caption" type="text" class="form-control" value=""/>
</div>
</form>
</div>
</div>
</section>
<section class="slide level2">

<p>PROJECT DETAIL:</p>
<p>A complex application has been developed to generate analytical tables and diagrams to summarize and visualize the stock or index performance. First, the Stock Quote selection will provide up-to-date stock or index information. Second, for a faster stock prediction, the Kalman Filter Prediction uses the fast Kalman Filter machine learning algorithm to predict tomorrows stock momentum, prices, and volume. For a slower prediction, the Stock Forecast selection uses a variety of machine learning algorithms for prediction. Moreover, there are 7 analytical stock analysis tools such as MACD, SMA, OBV, RSI, AROON, and etc to help the investor to visualize the future performance of the stock or index. Finally, the Stock Summary selection will summarize the stock prediction and analysis in a table and diagram.</p>
</section>
<section class="slide level2">

<p>USER INTERFACE:</p>
<p>The application takes the stock or index symbol from the user such as Google(GOOG) or Facebook(FB). Next, the user has to select one of the following choices from the menu:</p>
<pre><code>Stock Quote
Stock Moving Average Convergence Divergence
Stock Simple Moving Averages
Stock On Balance Volume
Stock Accumulation Distribution Line
Stock Average Directional Index
Stock Aroon Indicator
Stock Relative Strength Index
Stock Stochastic Oscillator
Stock Kalman Filter Prediction
Stock Forecast
Stock Analysis Summary</code></pre>
<p>Finally, the user can select the number of days to analyze or predict a particular stock or index, ranging from 55 days to 2,600 days in a slider.</p>
</section>
